## Import

New Relic Service Levels can be imported using a concatenated string of the format
 `<account_id>:<sli_id>:<guid>`, where the <span pulumi-lang-nodejs="`guid`" pulumi-lang-dotnet="`Guid`" pulumi-lang-go="`guid`" pulumi-lang-python="`guid`" pulumi-lang-yaml="`guid`" pulumi-lang-java="`guid`">`guid`</span> is the entity the SLI relates to.

Example:

```bash
$ terraform import newrelic_service_level.foo 12345678:4321:MXxBUE18QVBQTElDQVRJT058MQ
```

